data.description: This stunning is  Andrea model home with 5 bedrooms, 4 baths and a 3-car garage. Ideal, 3,818 SqFt floorplan offers a first-floor master, a guest bedroom on main level, a formal living room with a dramatic 2 story ceiling, a formal dining room, family room and a loft. Chef's kitchen is equipped with 42'' cabinets with crown molding, granite counters & backsplash, center island, double oven, snack bar and a family dining area. The master retreat boasts a tray ceiling, door to the patio, his and hers walk-in closets, dual sinks, a garden tub and a walk-in shower. This light and airy home features neutral tile laid on the diagonal, high-hat lighting and accordion shutters. Enjoy quiet time on the patio overlooking your large yard with new custom pool, a waterfall and tropical landscaping. AC's are 2020 and 2022. Please see attachment for full list of upgrades. The clubhouse offers a beautiful pool, tennis and pickle ball courts, basketball, ping-pong, billiards, library, entertaining kitchen, a fully- equipped gym for all levels of exercise, and children's play area and swim area.  This is truly resort living with out the resort prices!!
